        Retrieve employee information, calculate pay based on shift and pay type.
        Parameters:
        name - the Employee's name.
        position - the type of work the employee is responsible for.
        salary - True or false regarding the pay type of the employee.
        pay - Hourly pay rate of the employee.
        shift - First, second or third shift.
        date - The date the employee began work.
